          Pardo et al., IEEE, Trans. Ant. Prop., Vol 49, No 12,
          pp. 1683-1694, 2001.

	* aii/aii_color_table.pro: change in ciolors to get them darker
	  (no yellow or zyan in the first 12 colors) for a better 
          contrast in color plots.

