2002-03-17  Thomas Kuhn  <tkuhn@uni-bremen.de>

        * arts-1-0-12

        * src: update of O2 functions in continua.cc since the 
        standard models use fixed VMR-O2. This is now changed to 
        variable VMR according to the input VMR profile.

        * src: additional models in continua.cc implemented. These are
        (1) CKD2.4 with its special version for the mm frequency range 
        (gives same values as Rosenkranz, Radio Science, 1998) (see variable 
        ivc in function CKD24_H20) and 
        (2) then N2-N2 rototranslatioal CIA absorption model of Borysow
        and Frommhold, Astrophys. Journal, 1986.

        * src: in m_abs.cc change of the functions h2o_absSet and n2_absSet.
        Now if no H2O or N2 tag is detected are the values of h2o_abs and 
        n2_abs automatically set to zero. 

        * aii: additional and updates of several idl functions.  

